     'c:.c.h,yacc:.y,asm:.s.S,java:.java,cpp:.c++.cc.cpp.cxx.hxx.hpp.C.H,php:.php.php3.phtml'.

`copy_files'(boolean)
     Copy files instead of linking.  When the `-f' option is used,
     htags make links of tag files in `cgi-bin' directory by default.

